Finally, we discuss the accuracy of our method. Given a reference solution $\left\{X^I(z;N_{\rm max}), \rho(N_{\rm max})\right\}$ obtained with a high resolution $N_{\rm max}$, the numerical error of the solution $\left\{X^I(z;N), \mu(N)\right\}$ is defined by

